 \int_{-\pi}^\pi \frac{\cos\varphi}{1-k\cos\varphi} \, d\varphi = \int_{-\infty}^{\infty}\frac{\frac{1-x^2}{1+x^2}}{1-k\frac{1-x^2}{1+x^2}} \cdot\frac{2\,dx}{1+x^2} 
